episodes.title: Inside Carbon Nation: What life was like for me as a woman in the cult
episodes.description:
Here I share what life was like for me before joining the cult, and my 5-year experience as a woman inside of Carbon Nation up to the moment I left the destructive cult. 

For educational purposes only. 

I share to bring awareness to destructive cults and high control groups. I also share to provide a safe place to discuss how people get involved in these situations and to inspire hope that there is recovery and life after leaving. 

Thank you or listening (:

episodes.title: WHY cult members do what they do - EXPOSING the tactics of destructive cult leader Eligio Bishop
episodes.description: Discussing cult tactics, cult leaders, deception, coercive control, and more. I specifically speak from my experience in the cult, Carbon Nation ,which I was directly involved in for five years.
